{"tid":1381234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［精華］梁天琦獄中書信重點","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:24:45.000Z","uid":288912,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e80735c44ee274b9d79a3104d493f2c814cffb","tid":1381234,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"以下幾節好重要：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家應該首先照顧自己情緒。</span></span>近日好多人唔開心，但因為想做多啲嘢，忽略自己感受同信念，反而會令個心唔堅定而判斷錯誤。唔止仇恨，恐懼都好阻頭阻勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建立自衛武力嘅合理依據</span></span>。唔還手固然係只有捱打，但還手之後畀人抽後腳，唔止好唔公平，對運動亦無幫助。有法律同輿論上嘅武力依據，市民人身安全先有希望受保障<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">當本應解決社會問題的人選擇冷待，反而熱衷於將香港的命運放上賭桌作政治豪賭，我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壞人死之前唔好畀自己死。</span></span>諗吓有冇辦法用啲港豬同藍絲李代桃僵，而唔係好人同壞人玉石俱焚<br />\n<br />\n開放討論&amp;廣傳"},{"pid":"2fc6ecc4ca0b4eae0dd91190fc0f0ec20a3a88eb","tid":1381234,"uid":25573,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"天琦叫我地be water呀，唔好放棄自己生命！"},{"pid":"48e06485de9f4f58e0282fc8a9b4919df09c8811","tid":1381234,"uid":208452,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"40b408b9e4a74e224eeed53558e04eb9cfc503e5","tid":1381234,"uid":169999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4173c567a2478ed8a2a9e6cc1fb8accf7ba4647","tid":1381234,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"5380dde7327fa7aa1cb4a66d24b2edaaca722e43","tid":1381234,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48e06485de9f4f58e0282fc8a9b4919df09c8811","tid":1381234,"uid":208452,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"歷史工作做得好，就畀到以武制暴嘅理據"},{"pid":"8b576163dec25743f866cac0b2dcecd453c18c31","tid":1381234,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:00:13.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"ba28b1199be3276160a2c183101495a7f9240b64","tid":1381234,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"589e12d779faf3e6b6b841fb56431c2403c15800","tid":1381